      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-item">
      <h3>Cake Pops & Cakesicles</h3>
      <p>
        Cake pops are <strong>$3 each</strong> (<strong>$36 per dozen</strong>).
        Cakesicles are <strong>$4 each</strong>. Themed designs, characters, or intricate details may affect final pricing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-item">
      <h3>Dubai Chocolate Bars</h3>
      <p>
        Small: <strong>$10</strong> · Medium: <strong>$20</strong> · Large: <strong>$30</strong> · Jumbo: <strong>$40</strong>.
